title:
q-Calculus and Convolution Techniques in the Study Of q-Ruscheweyeh
  Derivatives With Janowski Functions
abstract:
In this paper, we use concept of q-calculus and technique of convolution to
study the q-Ruscheweyeh derivative by the concept of Janowski function, then we
define new Subclass of analytic functions. Coefficients Estimates, radii of
starlikeness, close to convexity, extreme points and many interesting
properties are investigate, obtained and studied.
